title: Toolbox co. wins trade war, so where are the sales?
text:
Toolbox co. wins trade war, so where are the sales? 3:01pm IST - 01:58 
American company Metal Box International should be one of the winners of a little-known trade-war over toolboxes. But so far, it hasn’t worked out that way.
